VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \bSecCertificateCopyData\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:SecCertificateCopyPublicKey|SecCertificateCopyKey|SecKeyRef|publicKeyHash|spki|SubjectPublicKeyInfo
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects certificate pinning implementations that copy leaf certificate data without extracting and pinning the public key.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Certificate Pinning Using Leaf Certificate Hash Only.
